        "type": "Activity",
        "activityType": "observational-study",
        "name": "Multi-centre VAD registry observational data collection",
        "description": "Retrospective extraction of in-vivo hemolysis indices from a 47-centre implant registry. No experimental controls were imposed; patient allocation, device settings, and measurement timing were determined by clinical practice rather than by a pre-specified experimental protocol. Data were filtered post-hoc to the five target operating points using nearest-neighbour matching on pump speed and flow rate.",
        "startedAtTime": "2024-06-01T00:00:00Z",
        "endedAtTime": "2025-01-15T00:00:00Z"
      },
      "metricValue": 0.17,
      "metricUnit": "fractional NIH deviation",
      "passed": true
    },
    {
