      "rationale": "Registry data matched to COU operating points via nearest-neighbour; actual deviations range up to ±14% on flow rate. Blood analogue viscosity not controlled in registry; estimated population variability ±30%. Conditions are insufficiently controlled relative to a prospective experiment."
    },
